metadata.name: Underground S2 Access Pass
metadata.description:
A private, members-only collective of 555 talented traders and investors looking to disrupt and define NFT culture. Membership to the organization and all benefits until June 30, 2024 come from holding the Underground S2 Access Pass NFT. Art created by toomuchlag.

Disclaimer: Shared accounts or mirroring our information to another server or community will result in an immediate ban and removal of your pass without refund or warning.
